      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-mrl5-full-validation",
      "rationale": "CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) operates under ISO 9001:2015-certified QMS. Full software validation suite executed: 47 benchmark cases with documented pass/fail records, version-controlled source, automated regression testing on each release, traceable build artifacts. SQA documentation package reviewed and approved by independent assessor."
